=================================
Installing NfQuery Framework
=================================

Development
-----------

If you want to develop for NfQuery or use the latest code we're working on,
you can clone and install from the github repository.

        $ git clone https://github.com/ulakbim/nfquery


Easy Install
------------
You can use the setuptools easy_install script to get NfQuery and other python modules on your system :

        $ sudo easy_install NfQuery
        $ sudo easy_install MySQLdb
        $ sudo easy_install txJSON-RPC
                    ......



MySQL
-----
You need to install MySQL Server 5.2 or newer version. Additional instructions : 

    1) Create a database named nfquery and a user with the same name whose all permissions on nfquery
    database.

    2) Import nfquery database with using nfquery.sql file placed in 'WHERE IS IT!!' 
    by using the command : 
            
                    mysql -u nfquery -p nfquery < nfquery.sql

    3) ....


